query: UPDATE activations SET status = 'completed' WHERE id IN (SELECT id FROM (SELECT id FROM activations ORDER BY createdAt DESC LIMIT 2) AS temp); UPDATE activations SET status = 'cancelled' WHERE id IN (SELECT id FROM (SELECT id FROM activations ORDER BY createdAt DESC LIMIT 2 OFFSET 2) AS temp); UPDATE activations SET status = 'expired' WHERE id IN (SELECT id FROM (SELECT id FROM activations ORDER BY createdAt DESC LIMIT 2 OFFSET 4) AS temp); UPDATE activations SET status = 'active' WHERE id IN (SELECT id FROM (SELECT id FROM activations ORDER BY createdAt DESC LIMIT 2 OFFSET 6) AS temp);
